  <h1><span class="the">The</span> 2014 Meedan.org Annual Report</h1>

  <div class="fleuron">&#10086;</div>

  <p class="intro">Meedan is a hybrid nonprofit/for-profit organization. We share code, people, offices, and values across two companies: <em>Meedan.org</em> is a registered 501(c) 3 established in 2006 that works on non-commercial projects to support global journalism. <em>Meedan Labs</em> is a for-profit spun off in 2014 to develop software for collaborative social media translation. This Annual Report reflects the state of Meedan.org and its financial health.
  </p>
